<p begin='00:05:58.425' end='00:06:00.827' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>CERTAINLY TO ONE WOMAN IN THE<br/>AUDIENCE.</span></p>
<p begin='00:06:00.861' end='00:06:06.867' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>[LAUGHTER]<br/>WHO SEEMINGLY FORGOT THAT SHE</span></p>
